I have said so many NO’s when it comes to food for my children.

The best part of my day is often sitting down to breakfast with my children. We all have a sweet tooth and like all children they love sugary breakfast cereals. I’m always searching for better cereals and breakfast options - most are full of maida and refined sugar.  Meals for children need not be dessert.

This is why I ❤️ this video - @anushkasharma and @slurrpfarm have captured the NO-YES-NO of all of our homes. It’s not hard to say YES when you can see zero-junk food made only with millets and wholesome ingredients. Way to go Slurrp Farm! Seriously, #YesKaTimeAaGaya
